title: Exception thrown when exporting data from a table containing a highlight/map
description: When trying to export data from an attached report, an exception is thrown. This issue occurs when attempting to export data from a table that contains a highlight or map. To reproduce the issue, follow these steps:
OB: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from a table that contains a highlight or map.
EB: When exporting data from a table, the expected behavior is that the data should be exported without any errors or exceptions.
SR:
1. Open the attached report.
2. Locate a table that contains a highlight or map.
3. Attempt to export the data from this table.
4. Observe the exception occurring during the export process.
